dcterms:description: The Abalone dataset consists of 4177 samples with 9 features each, including Rings (the target variable), Length, Diameter, Height, WholeWeight, ShuckedWeight, VisceraWeight, ShellWeight, and Sex. The dataset is used to predict the age of abalones based on physical measurements.
dcterms:title: Abalone Dataset
